~*~Goddess of the hunt and the Moon~*~</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenhera.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Queen Hera</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Queen of the Gods</span><br>  Posts: 81<br> <font color=#993300>(6/11/01 1:50:41 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=224.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Hermes?</span><hr size=1> Hera turned her gaze to Artemis.  &quot;Hermes?,&quot; she scrowled.  &quot;Where did this one come from.&quot; Now her mind was racing...someone somehow decived her and was able to hide a birth from her.  Her eyebrows narrowed. &quot;Who is she?&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uo0ohestiao0o.showPublicProfile?language=EN>o0o hestia o0o</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 29<br> <font color=#993300>(6/11/01 4:08:08 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=224.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A New Temple in Themiscrya</span><hr size=1> ~in a burst of white light which consumed miles of land Hestia appears~<br>
